      "position": "Wing",
      "nationality": "England",
      "blurb": "England wing and 2025 Lions Test starter; serial hat-trick scorer (four vs Saracens, hat-tricks vs Bath, Clermont, Leinster) and the first Englishman to score in every round of a Six Nations. Aerial dominance, finishing instinct, and centre-grade footwork",
      "indexHigh": [
